ts/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個求學生涯好撚痛苦<br />\n仲要d同學都係死mk成日俾人洽<br />\n幾經辛苦考完會考,點知有d死mk仲高分過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時聽到d係外國住/讀書既fd講果邊做低下階層都有基本保障<br />\n係日本做便利店都生活到,係養唔到家咁解<br />\n睇下香港便利店人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再聽埋人地係美國讀書<br />\n由小學開始教學方式已經同香港係兩個世界<br />\n真係覺得自己好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早知細個就搵d興趣發展或者索性玩撚哂佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88abe08f41f3c62d598c4fbdc151e52af218ee2a","tid":1142930,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"發現自己真係好鍾意數學<br />\n不過...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32412729a0c900e584ce961939f804ac3da16ce9","tid":1142930,"uid":136061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:50:50.000Z","msg":"發覺就算你讀到書，你柒毒唔識交際面面俱圓都係霉架喇，好撚多開鋪既老細冇讀書係佔多數"},{"pid":"d123b1f0c6eda71e100d76bd7737040104acacce","tid":1142930,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1658e9a954172c8cd07110329ebe79a6ce566c91","tid":1142930,"uid":165336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:30:40.000Z","msg":"係香港出世但唔適合讀書真係好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係果D壞學生,我以前真係乖到仆街<br />\n上堂都唔訓功課都絕小會抄人<br />\n連頭髮都自動會剪,雖然我好撚憎d垃圾規矩<br />\n但係唔想好似班mk咁成日俾人捉咁麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上堂都係聽書,日日都補習<br />\n數碼暴龍叮噹我都係斷斷續續咁睇<br />\n但好明顯係有D類似而家d人講sen果d問題<br />\n以前冇人理